orts desk\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So will their fortunes continue to decline at Paris 2024?\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999947497145, \"rank\": 5.2503058640640455e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their fortunes\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or will Team GB bounce back at the closest thing to another home Olympics?\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Team GB\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"the closest thing\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"another home Olympics\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We examined three rigorously researched medal projections for Team GB in Paris - and the most striking aspect is probably how alike they are.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999758772066007, \"rank\": 1.6207702474206625e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996384615969, \"rank\": 3.6153864227003367e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three rigorously researched medal projections\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the most striking aspect\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"UK Sport, the body responsible for distributing funding, forecasts that British athletes will win between 50 and 70 medals at this summer's Games.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1254, \"end\": 1262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1326, \"end\": 1333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.994975851753584, \"rank\": 0.004843265383799194, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"between 50 and 70 medals\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Games\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB hit that range at each of the last four Olympics, ranging from 51 at Beijing 2008 to 67 in Rio, which set and remains a record.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999758772066007, \"rank\": 1.6207702474206625e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9926359810594878, \"rank\": 0.007415688401991513, \"text\": \"Beijing 2008\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1501, \"end\": 1504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9